<br>
 Dear Ares,<br>
<br>
 Your favored assassin has died. Don't go and mourn now. I'm sure some amazon will be by to tell you where and when you can say goodbye, and such. I'm not one for goodbyes, but I'll see you again soon. Don't go and find a replacement.<br>
<br>
 Dawnithinia Rivent Darkshade. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uareslordofwar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ares Lord of War</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 74<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(11/26/01 9:05:31 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Death Letter To The Gods</span><hr size=1> Ares finding the scroll unraveled it and read its contents. Standing shocked for a few minutes, waves of emotions for once crashing threw the almost always emotionless god. He couldn't understand it, tearing the scroll up he threw the pieces on the ground. Smashed statues, tapestries and vases.Then he spoke to no-one in particular<br>
<br>
&quot;You didn't need to die, why did you DIE!&quot; he remembers the last two lines of the scroll.<br>
<br>
&quot;You'll be back I know you will but now would be good. I'll take care of your son. But you need to know something, you made me laugh and I guess we were friends...o.k I know we were. But I need you back...you'd better come back Dawn&quot;<br>
<br>
With that he sank to his knees in the temple of War and jsut knelt there for a long time, emotionless. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessage?topicID=192.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessage?topicID=201.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.emailToFriend?topicID=199.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.threadControl?topicID=199.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=199.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=199.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsuniteamazonsunitescrollboard">Amazons Unite Scroll Board<option value="amazonsunitefrm32">The Mythical Odyssey<option value="amazonsunitefrm23">The Olympian Gods<option value="amazonsunitefrm15">Black Sea Tavern and Inn<option value="amazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya">Sisters of Themiscrya<option value="amazonsunitefrm6">Amazons of the Northern Lands<option value="amazonsunitefrm8">